      • newReadOnlyTransaction

        public final DOMStoreReadTransaction newReadOnlyTransaction()
        已过时。 
        从接口复制的说明: DOMStoreTransactionChain
        Create a new read only transaction which will continue the chain. The previous write transaction has to be either READY or CANCELLED.

        If previous write transaction was already commited to data store, new read-only transaction is same as obtained via DOMStoreTransactionFactory.newReadOnlyTransaction() and contains merged result of previous one and current state of data store.

        Otherwise read-only transaction presents isolated view as if previous read-write transaction was successful. State which was introduced by other transactions outside this transaction chain after creation of previous transaction is not visible.

        指定者:
        newReadOnlyTransaction 在接口中 DOMStoreTransactionChain
        指定者:
        newReadOnlyTransaction 在接口中 DOMStoreTransactionFactory
        返回:
        New transaction in the chain.
        另请参阅:
        for more information.

      • newReadWriteTransaction

        public final DOMStoreReadWriteTransaction newReadWriteTransaction()
        已过时。 
        从接口复制的说明: DOMStoreTransactionChain
        Create a new read write transaction which will continue the chain. The previous read-write transaction has to be either COMMITED or CANCELLED.

        If previous write transaction was already commited to data store, new read-write transaction is same as obtained via DOMStoreTransactionFactory.newReadWriteTransaction() and contains merged result of previous one and current state of data store.

        Otherwise read-write transaction presents isolated view as if previous read-write transaction was successful. State which was introduced by other transactions outside this transaction chain after creation of previous transaction is not visible.

        指定者:

        指定者:
